metadata.name: BAKENEKO ~ Lunatic Love~
metadata.description:
" BAKENEKO ~ Lunatic Love~ "

She "devours" the man she fell in love with in order to make it her own.
unsatisfied heart.   Lunatic Love.
● The bakeneko "changed cat" is a type of Japanese yōkai. 
● Their ability to deceive humans comes from harnessing the psychic energy of the moon.

I am influenced by classical expressions such as Japanese ukiyoe.
The artist depicts bewitching women (yokai) with modern interpretations and techniques.
